Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Mr. Ryu, standby okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, standby for docking.\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in, Mr. Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2... 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser searcher synchronized.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam B Parts released!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Core Change! Docking, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After deserting the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...Amuro may never train like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The battleship Gwazine\Nhad departed from Granada...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...a Zeon frontline base on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It belonged to Rear Admiral Kycilia Zabi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...eldest daughter of the Zabi family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...and commander of Zeon's\NMobile Assault Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kycilia was visiting M'Quve,\Nwho supervised the mining of resources...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...which were considered vital\Nto both the Federation and Zeon forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The war effort had continued\Nregardless of the White Base's troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeon's Secret Mine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do\Nif Amuro comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you know,\Na deserter would certainly be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You must be lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what military regulations dictate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you think of doing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...to someone who's fought at your side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means we can do it if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that, Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Fraw Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand why Amuro left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I ask him to come back to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Fraw Bow. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not regular military here,\Nso we'd never do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...we can't continue to overlook\NAmuro's selfish behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's true that he's\Nbehaving pretty badly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Fraw Bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, take me along too!\N- I want to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't come. This isn't a joy ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to look for Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You think she can convince him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all a question of timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that big brother Amuro\Nis a V.S.O.P?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,V.S.O.P?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't you know?\NIt means, 'very important person'.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Maybe I got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let them do anythlng foollsh to Amuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll take responslblllty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll guarantee It, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll go and flnd hlm, won't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! I shouldn't have barged in like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this thing\Nwhat everyone's worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll forgive you if you go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai says deserters\Nare punishable by death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's how everyone really feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Leave!\N- You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone aboard the White Base\Nneeds your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Running away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that you're not confident\Nthat everyone will accept you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you can't go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do we have to sit here doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go anywhere\Nuntil Fraw Bow's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get moving again,\Nwe can just tell her where we went.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they say Central Asia\Nis neutral territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...but there're a lot of Zeons around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they intercept our radio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When Amuro gets back, I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting a metallic response at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking,\Nstopping so suddenly?! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She should just go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We get two grams in a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a good quality Solium deposit,\Njust as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can find five more deposits like this,\Nour forces will be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not only about Solium.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation must not get even\None gram of any precious resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what will lead us\Nto a decisive victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...and will also establish our control\Nafter the war is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's another slmllar deposlt{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make sure you have all the men{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this was the Zeon mine!\NI finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you tell me what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shout like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Zeon mining base there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No! What if they see you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude! I'm not that careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta tell the White Base about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! If the enemy hears our transmission,\Nwe'll be at a disadvantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw, you go back to the White Base\Nand tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about you, Amuro?\N- I'll stay here and continue observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,3 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Marker, any message?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If the enemy found us here,\Nwe'd make an easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We know. Don't take your eyes off\Nthe sonar searcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Any chance he's defected to Zeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd treat him like a hero\Nif he brings them the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- He is a deserter, after all.\N- Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the Zeon mine...\NGeneral Revil plans to take on Odessa Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have a single Zaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If I take this place out with Gundam,\Nthe Federation forces won't have to mobilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright and Ms. Mirai\Nwon't mess around with me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's going on?!\N- Lady Kycilia, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to tell them, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm spotted, I'll have to deal with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare Adzam for launch at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,M'Quve, I'm not sure if I can forgive you\Nfor failing to detect that mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies, Lady Kycilia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a good opportunity to test the Adzam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lady Kycilia. I certainly will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing the Federation's mobile suit\Nup close and in person...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be useful for our future strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it over...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,lts performance seems far superior\Nto what Garma's data suggested.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,M'Quve, approach it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's above me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the higher ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch the Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Surface temperature, 4,000 degrees?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because of that sand-like stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Releaslng 98% of all energy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...for pllot and clrcult protectlon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,98%?!\NI won't be able to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A base near something that looks\Nlike a mine? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't quite match the location...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the Federation estimates\Nwhich General Revil told us about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not making this up! I saw it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we can't just ignore it.\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's working, Lady Kycilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we do have more experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...in mobile suit research.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The magnetic radiation field is weakening.\NFinish him off quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offenslve energy reduced.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can move, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He deflected it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A Zaku would have been crippled by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry! Shake him off!\N- Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to dump me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy the base before our secrets get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But there are still soldiers there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our state secrets are the priority now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The base... exploded...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They abandoned... the base...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Its performance is greater than rumored.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have to speed up\Nthe deployment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...of all the mobile suits we're testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation was gonna hit this Zeon base\Nwith all of its force, and I destroyed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This one isn't any good, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All data systems have been\Ncompletely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"No. 102 Mining Base..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the No. 102 Mining Base?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean what I destroyed\Nwas just one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...of many mining bases?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So this isn't the mine that General Revil\Nis trying to take down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a mine even bigger than this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just someone passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a Federation or Zeon\Nrescue crew soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The bleeding's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use it if you see help arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Think they'll come so soon?\NA rescue...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't lose hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you said you were\Nthe pilot of that mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd find it hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you are, don't go soft on your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have enough lives for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not enough lives, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's confirm. Approach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow...\NAre you sure this is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the Gundam do all this on its own?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of any other possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But... this wasn't their main base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was, It wouldn't have fallen\Nwith the Gundam alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's caused quite a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's safe to say that,\Nbecause of the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...the enemy will be on guard\Nand digging their heels in hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro must think he's a hero\Nright about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- But I can't see him anywhere.\N- He ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.24,0:22:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his problem...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does Amuro think he is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:22:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no idea how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro sees his foes up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ral's troops are planning\Nan attack on the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Gundam's beam rifle\Nhits the Gouf...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...the enemy laughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NRamba Ral's Attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral's Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:53.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:58.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:09.13,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:14.05,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:18.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:24.06,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:28.65,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:38.95,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:53.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:58.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:09.13,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:14.05,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:18.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:24.06,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:28.65,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:38.95,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
